headline: Like wine, perfect Kellanova cracker pairings bring spark to holiday parties
summary: The holiday season is upon us, and who doesn't have at least one party or gathering on the calendar? Whether hosting or bringing a snack to add to the table, knowing how to pair your crackers with the right cheeses and meats can evoke compliments and happy guests.
